            <title>[HBASE-652] dropping table fails silently if table isn&apos;t disabled</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-652</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Rather than fail silently, hbase should throw an exception&lt;/p&gt;</description>
